  "term": "thm:preimage-ops",
  "kind": "Theorem",
  "title": "Preimages Preserve Set Operations",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $f : A \\to B$ and $S, T \\subseteq B$. Then\n- [label=(\\roman*)]\n- $f^{-1}(S \\cup T) = f^{-1}(S) \\cup f^{-1}(T)$,\n- $f^{-1}(S \\cap T) = f^{-1}(S) \\cap f^{-1}(T)$,\n- $f^{-1}(S \\setminus T) = f^{-1}(S) \\setminus f^{-1}(T)$,\n- $f^{-1}(S^c) = (f^{-1}(S))^c$.",
